snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin' VS Camellia 2.5 FULL WEEK | Bob TakeOver (FNF Mod/Hard/Remix)
snippet.description:
Friday Night Funkin' VS CAMELLIA 2.5 (FULL WEEK) + Secret songs in Freeplay for the PC in 2160p Ultra HD. VS. Camellia is based around Camellia's music.
LiterallyNoOne - Director/Official OST: https://youtu.be/ZQ9KizWj6QY

I am just going to play the new songs and show off whatever I see new like the arts, Bob TakeOver, 3 extra songs, and the new playable characters. I thought I'd never see Bob from onslaught, literally every fnf mod ever Vs Bob again but here we are facing him. It is an official crossover since Wiley gave them permission to use the character. This is Bob's 2nd takeover, the first one being when he took over Bob & Bosip.

Camellia Official - Music:
https://www.youtube.com/user/camelliaxxglitch
LiterallyNoOne - VS CAMELLIA 2.5 OFFICIAL OST:
https://youtu.be/ZQ9KizWj6QY
Vs Camellia 2.5 Download (Go break your fingers):
https://gamebanana.com/mods/290601
https://gamejolt.com/games/VSCamellia/733937

Game Note:  This mod adds a brand new week (Bob TakeOver), with a character selection screen and new art.

REMINDER: If Hard Mode's too difficult, you can always try the Normal / Easy difficulties!
